Ni–o years.


283
0:36:23,44 --> 0:36:30,13
The colony is a busy place as couples take
turns flying out over the ocean in search


284
0:36:30,13 --> 0:36:35,64
of food.


285
0:36:35,64 --> 0:36:40,9
Because frigates lack the oils in their feathers
