308
0:39:36,24 --> 0:39:42,19
The abundance of food at the surface has also
drawn the largest fish in the ocean, the whale


309
0:39:42,19 --> 0:39:44,15
shark.


310
0:39:44,15 --> 0:39:55,97
Moving slowly along, they take in big gulps
of water, then filter out zooplankton, krill,


311
0:39:55,97 --> 0:39:58,15
larvae, and even small fish.


312
0:39:58,15 --> 0:40:9,9
At up to 30 tons and 20 meters in length,
