327
0:42:8,619 --> 0:42:18,28
the protective shelter of the rocky shoreline.
Here, they learn to interact with other sea


328
0:42:18,28 --> 0:42:29,44
lions, to vocalize, to swim, and hunt.


329
0:42:29,44 --> 0:42:39,18
Being a young sea lion is all about riding
the currents and waves and investigating the


